The paper discusses privacy threats in centralized processing of data in IoT and smart environments, and proposes Secure Multiparty Computation (SMC) as a solution. This suggests that the paper could belong to the categories of cryptography (cs.CR), distributed computing (cs.DC), databases (cs.DB), social and information networks (cs.SI), or computer and society (cs.CY). However, since the focus is on privacy and security, cs.CR is the most likely category. The other categories are also relevant as they deal with aspects such as distributed processing, data management, and social implications of technology.
